因為...你們這麼不一樣
Because......you're so different.

611
01:17:01,840 --> 01:17:03,510
你們是這麼的完美
You're so perfect.

612
01:17:06,310 --> 01:17:07,350
是的
Yes.

613
01:17:08,470 --> 01:17:10,430
你是哪一代的？
What generation are you?

614
01:17:19,150 --> 01:17:20,560
Nexus 6型
Nexus 6.

615
01:17:20,860 --> 01:17:22,230
啊，我就知道!
Ah, I knew it.

616
01:17:22,820 --> 01:17:25,990
因為我為泰瑞爾公司做基因設計工作
Because I do genetic design work for the Tyrell Corporation.

617
01:17:26,170 --> 01:17:28,120
你們有我的一部份
There's some of me in you.

618
01:17:29,580 --> 01:17:31,250
給我展示一下
Show me something.

619
01:17:31,620 --> 01:17:32,920
