Like what?

620
01:17:33,520 --> 01:17:34,420
什麼都行
Like anything.

621
01:17:37,130 --> 01:17:40,270
我們不是電腦，賽巴斯汀，我們有形有質
We're no computers, Sebastian. We're physical.

622
01:17:43,840 --> 01:17:47,390
我思考，賽巴斯汀……故我在
I think, Sebastian......therefore, I am.

623
01:17:48,760 --> 01:17:51,230
非常好，普莉絲，現在給他看看為什麼
Very good, Pris. Now show him why.

624
01:18:19,090 --> 01:18:20,620
我們有許多共通點
We've got a lot in common.

625
01:18:20,920 --> 01:18:21,960
你是什麼意思？
What do you mean?

626
01:18:22,050 --> 01:18:23,440
相似的問題
Similar problems.

627
01:18:23,550 --> 01:18:25,340
加速衰老
Accelerated decrepitude.

628
01:18:28,050 --> 01:18:31,600
我對生化機械所知不多，羅伊，我希望我知道
I don't know much about bio-mechanics, Roy. I wish I did.

629
01:18:32,890 --> 01:18:34,980
要是我們不盡快找人幫忙
If we don't find help soon...

630
01:18:35,540 --> 01:18:38,040
普莉絲就活不久了
...Pris hasn't got long to live.

631
01:18:38,680 --> 01:18:40,320
我們不能容許這樣
We can't allow that.

632
01:18:42,690 --> 01:18:44,990
- 他厲害嗎？　- 誰？
-Is he good?　-Who?

633
01:18:46,050 --> 01:18:48,280
- 你的對手　- 哦...泰瑞爾博士？
-Your opponent.　-Oh, Dr. Tyrell?

634
01:18:49,500 --> 01:18:53,200
我下棋只擊敗過他一次，他是個天才
I've only beaten him once in chess. He's a genius.

635
01:18:55,400 --> 01:18:56,920
他設計了你們
He designed you.

636
01:18:58,540 --> 01:19:00,340
也許他能幫忙
Maybe he could help.

637
01:19:01,500 --> 01:19:04,300
我很樂意向他提出
I'd be happy to mention it to him.

638
01:19:06,170 --> 01:19:08,640
最好是我能親自和他談
Better if I talk to him in person.

639
01:19:12,890 --> 01:19:16,640
不過我瞭解到，他是那類不易見到的人
But I understand he's a sort of hard man to get to.

640
01:19:17,980 --> 01:19:20,690
是的，很難
Yes. Very.

641
01:19:24,720 --> 01:19:26,320
你會幫我們嗎？
Will you help us?

642
01:19:27,850 --> 01:19:28,990
我不能
I can't.

643
01:19:29,320 --> 01:19:30,980
我們需要你，賽巴斯汀
We need you, Sebastian.

644
01:19:31,520 --> 01:19:33,140
你是我們最好的也是唯一的朋友
You're our best and only friend.

645
01:19:47,220 --> 01:19:49,380
我們很高興你找到我們
We're so happy you found us.

646
01:19:51,740 --> 01:19:56,180
我認為世上沒有別的人類會幫助我們
I don't think there's another human being in the whole world who would've helped us.

647
01:20:45,230 --> 01:20:48,610
六萬六千 普塞安科維奇
66,000 Prosser & Ankovich.

648
01:20:49,900 --> 01:20:53,870
- 交易，交易價...    - 藍色入口
-Trade. Trade at two...   -Blue entry

649
