吃掉皇后
... takes queen.

661
01:21:59,010 --> 01:22:00,580
你打什麼主意，賽巴斯汀？
What's on your mind, Sebastian?

662
01:22:01,600 --> 01:22:02,980
你在想什麼？
What are you thinking about?

663
01:22:04,810 --> 01:22:08,230
主教移到國王七，將死
Bishop to king seven. Checkmate.

664
01:22:09,480 --> 01:22:12,280
主教移到國王七，將死，我認為
Bishop to king seven. Checkmate, I think.

665
01:22:13,400 --> 01:22:15,910
頭腦風暴了，賽巴斯汀？
Got a brainstorm, huh, Sebastian?

666
01:22:16,490 --> 01:22:19,120
牛奶和餅乾讓你睡不著?
Milk and cookies kept you awake, huh?

667
01:22:19,730 --> 01:22:21,370
我們來討論一下
Let's discuss this.

668
01:22:22,000 --> 01:22:23,910
你還是上來吧，賽巴斯汀
You better come up, Sebastian.

669
01:22:41,680 --> 01:22:43,060
泰瑞爾先生？
Mr. Tyrell?

670
