我帶了個朋友
I brought a friend.

672
01:22:55,280 --> 01:22:58,410
我很驚訝你沒有早點來
I'm surprised you didn't come here sooner.

673
01:23:06,040 --> 01:23:08,880
要見你的製造者並不容易
It's not an easy thing to meet your maker.

674
01:23:10,400 --> 01:23:12,170
他能為你做什麼呢？
And what can he do for you?

675
01:23:13,630 --> 01:23:16,050
製造者能修補他的造物嗎？
Can the maker repair what he makes?

676
01:23:17,300 --> 01:23:20,100
你想要...被修改嗎？
Would you like to be modified?

677
01:23:20,640 --> 01:23:22,010
留在這裏
Stay here.

678
01:23:27,770 --> 01:23:30,770
