Had in mind something a little more radical.

679
01:23:31,900 --> 01:23:33,070
什麼...
What...?

680
01:23:34,070 --> 01:23:35,550
看起來是什麼問題？
What seems to be the problem?

681
01:23:36,900 --> 01:23:37,900
死亡
Death.

682
01:23:38,250 --> 01:23:39,400
死亡
Death.

683
01:23:40,410 --> 01:23:43,610
恐怕這有點超出我的管轄範圍，你...
Well, I'm afraid that's a little out of my jurisdiction. You--

684
01:23:43,620 --> 01:23:45,500
我想要更多的生命...
I want more life...

685
01:23:46,580 --> 01:23:47,660
父親
father.

686
01:23:52,700 --> 01:23:54,170
生命的實情
The facts of life.

687
01:23:56,450 --> 01:23:58,600
要做出改變，在...
To make an alteration in the...

688
01:23:59,100 --> 01:24:01,770
...有機生物系統進化上，是毀滅性的
...evolvement of an organic life system is fatal.

689
01:24:02,200 --> 01:24:05,860
編碼序列一旦建立就不能修改
A coding sequence cannot be revised once it's been established.

690
01:24:05,930 --> 01:24:06,730
為什麼不行?
Why not?

691
01:24:06,810 --> 01:24:08,980
因為，在孕育的第二天
Because by the second day of incubation...

692
