Wouldn't obstruct replication, but it does give rise to an error in replication.

704
01:24:44,140 --> 01:24:48,680
因此...新形成的DNA串帶有一個變異
So that...the newly formed DNA strand carries a mutation...

705
01:24:48,770 --> 01:24:50,980
